{"tid":1105603,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[DLLM系列］林明禎辣衣媽媽穿得下！彎腰掉出雪乳","createTime":"2019-04-14T04:41:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T05:36:55.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fa1972fff40be47bbc7df80d4636a55a95d03591","tid":1105603,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T04:41:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/14/123957_d179ca54a9e50c966f2e968c0d5b8ab7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F14%2F123957_d179ca54a9e50c966f2e968c0d5b8ab7.png&h=a8652152&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/14/123958_7c7cd205d89381d33a5d9e5b9a0751f0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F14%2F123958_7c7cd205d89381d33a5d9e5b9a0751f0.png&h=99cc2ed6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/14/124000_95ead2d8f623b7c3427e3b77ff8beab6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F14%2F124000_95ead2d8f623b7c3427e3b77ff8beab6.png&h=9bb13f96&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/14/124002_398877c300fa04d99c31b441b3b330d8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F14%2F124002_398877c300fa04d99c31b441b3b330d8.png&h=124c4a20&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/14/124004_4ed5c935360c0737f2a7171437989b25.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F14%2F124004_4ed5c935360c0737f2a7171437989b25.png&h=b6e014b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「真人版娜美」稱號的大馬女星林明禎，有著甜美臉蛋跟32E的魔鬼身材，無邪笑容擄獲不少人的心，被不少男性視為女神。而女神不僅人美，更是一名孝女，近日適逢媽媽的生日，林明禎特地回馬來西亞幫忙慶生，更值得注意的是，媽媽竟俏皮穿起她的衣服，卻完全無違和，猶如姊妹般的樣貌，讓不少網友直呼羨慕。<br />\n<br />\n林明禎日前曾在IG上曬出海邊美照，只見畫面中的她，身穿一件連身綠色洋裝，中空低胸的設計，讓傲人雪乳以及小蠻腰一覽無遺，只見她靠在欄杆上眺望遠方，一轉身，性感S曲線全現形，雪白的肌膚，加上一頭亮麗的短髮，猶如仙女般空靈的外貌，讓不少網友全都戀愛了。<br />\n<br />\n不過，更值得注意的是，林明禎的媽媽也換上了同一套印有樹葉圖案的服裝，想不到今年要過53歲生日的林明禎媽媽，身材與28歲的林明禎一樣好，不僅合身穿下洋裝，腰線也不輸女兒，相當纖細，皮膚Q彈的她，整體狀況完全讓人猜不出真實年齡，稱羨不少網友。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林明禎媽媽不科學的樣貌，讓不少網友看了驚呼連連，更有部分網友看了母女的合照，忍不住抗議老天實在太不公平，紛紛羨慕留言：「真的超強基因」、「超級辣媽生日快樂」、「媽媽好美好年輕哦」、「顯瘦家族」、「根本是大姐吧！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/林明禎辣衣媽媽穿得下-彎腰掉出雪乳-064006520.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E6%9E%97%E6%98%8E%E7%A6%8E%E8%BE%A3%E8%A1%A3%E5%AA%BD%E5%AA%BD%E7%A9%BF%E5%BE%97%E4%B8%8B-%E5%BD%8E%E8%85%B0%E6%8E%89%E5%87%BA%E9%9B%AA%E4%B9%B3-064006520.html&d=3CWkRSL9Alw2F84R5nIU8r3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=8c73d6ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/林明禎辣衣媽媽穿得下-彎腰掉出雪乳-064006520.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f79b26999b2bd82afed9dadb44fbb4e16f55ca34","tid":1105603,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:26:42.000Z","msg":"佢老母風韻猶存 笑容可掬 分分鐘好屌過明禎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42de1db34d8380718aa346c74580d5a2e15be570","tid":1105603,"uid":52062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:29:25.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c79f605f81fbb9544c6789aa86911e3bb9f0049","tid":1105603,"uid":218977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco